code: @Override protected Endpoint createEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     ObjectHelper.notNull(remaining, "channel").     PubNubConfiguration pubNubConfiguration = new PubNubConfiguration().     pubNubConfiguration.setChannel(remaining).     setProperties(pubNubConfiguration, parameters).     PubNubEndpoint endpoint = new PubNubEndpoint(uri, this, pubNubConfiguration).     setProperties(endpoint, parameters).     return endpoint. }
